Business description: Kemao Industries Limited

Kemao Industries Limited is an Australia-based professional metal packaging solution provider. The Company specializes in the production and supply of tinplate and cold-rolled steel coils to the global market. It operates through the sale of the electrolytic tinplate products segment. The Companyâs products include Laminated Tinplate, Printed Tinplate, Tinplate Sheets and Tinplate Coils. Its tinplate is applicable and supplied to customers in diverse industries. It is mainly used as food and beverage cans, general line cans, paint cans, aerosols, tea cans, battery casing, engine oil filters and office appliances. Its cold-rolled steel coils as a semifinished material are widely supplied to other steel further processing industries, such as construction, automotive, household electronic appliances, furniture, machinery hardware, and others. The Companyâs production base and manufacturing center is located in the Jiangsu Province of China.
